qryUpdateNextPtGenCode.name: qryUpdateNextPtGenCode
qryUpdateNextPtGenCode.description: update next generated code for patient
qryUpdateNextPtGenCode.queryString: update NoGenCon set NumValue = :nextNo, CurPreFix = :prefix where idCode = 'PATNO'

qryUpdatePatient.name: qryUpdatePatient
qryUpdatePatient.queryString:
update ptdetail set title = :t_title, 
given = :t_given, 
surname = :t_surname, 
address1 = :t_address1, 
address2 = :t_address2, 
suburb=:t_suburb, 
postcode=:t_postcode, 
state = :t_state, 
phone_ah=:t_phone_ah, 
phone_bh=:t_phone_bh, 
mobile=rtrim(:t_mobile+' '), 
dob = :t_dob, 
medicareno = :t_medicareno, 
member_no=:t_member_no, 
email = :t_email, 
fundcode = :t_fundcode, 
birthplace=:t_birthplace,
vetaffno=:t_vetafno, 
referalsrc=:t_refRalSrc,
mediexpry=:t_medExpiry,
mcare_refn=:t_mcareRefNo, 
claimdtls=:t_claimDetails, 
feepositn =:t_feepositn,
datejoined=:t_dateJoined,
nextofkin=:t_nextofkin where patient_no = :t_patient_no

qryUpdatePatientNo.name: qryUpdatePatientNo
qryUpdatePatientNo.description: update patient number to login table
qryUpdatePatientNo.queryString: update x0152578 set patient_no = :patientNo where userid = :email

qryUpdatePtDetailRegStatus.name: qryUpdatePtDetailRegStatus
qryUpdatePtDetailRegStatus.queryString: update ptdetail_reg set ptdetailStatus=:t_ptdetailStatus where idno =:t_idno
